      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/al-kafi:7:3:57:4",
      "text": [
        " قَالَ رَسُولُ اللَّهِ ( صلى الله عليه وآله ) لِأُسَامَةَ بْنِ زَيْدٍ يَا أُسَامَةُ لَا تَشْفَعْ فِي حَدٍّ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "A number of our companions, from Sahl Bin Ziyad, from Ibn Abu Najran, from Musanna Al Hanaat, ",
          "Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> has said: ‘Rasool-Allah<sup>saww</sup> said to Asama Bin Zayd: ‘You cannot intercede regarding a Penalty (<span class=\"iTxt\">Hadd</span>)’."
        ]
